  "text": "An analysis-by-synthesis coder with backward LP analysis has been chosen to encode input audio frames in each subband [CITATION_1] [8]. These frames are reconstructed by filtering an excitation vector, which is a combination of vectors derived from a variable number of stochastic codebooks, through a short-term predictor synthesis filter,",
